		<abstract id="abstract">
			<title>Using the Android SQLite Database</title>
			<para> This tutorial describes how to use the SQLite database in
				Android applications. It also demonstrates how to use existing
				ContentProvider and how to define new ones. It also demonstrates the
				usage of the Loader framework which allows to load data
				asynchronously.
			</para>
			<para>
				The tutorial is
				based on
				Eclipse 4.2, Java 1.6
				and
				Android 4.2.
			</para>
		</abstract>
